                    "text": "At the start of your next turn, a tightly wound internal spring inside the clockwork ballista bolt deploys several bladed arms that last for 1 minute. Each creature who begins their turn in or moves through a 5-foot emanation from the original square of the targeted creature takes 4d8 slashing damage (DC 28 basic Reflex save) for the duration.",
